data.description: Did you know this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage split floor plan called the “Allex” by Dr Horton helped make Willow Walk one of the fastest selling communities in Palmetto? Now that home building in this part of the community is complete, you can enjoy sitting on your lanai and watching a variety of birds fly over the pond behind your home or grill out on your lanai without the sounds of construction disrupting your relaxation time. You won't hear any neighborhood traffic either because this home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac. With neighbors of all ages you’ll make friends as your furry friends make their way around the neighborhood or when you get a chance to enjoy the beautiful community pool overlooking a massive lake. This is a community that shows pride of ownership with well maintained yards and residents can be seen washing their cars, power washing their driveways or displaying their favorite football team flag on game day. It’s also comforting to know that several of the residents are law enforcement officers and first responders who chose Willow Walk the place they call home. Don’t miss this opportunity to make your move to a beautiful, active community that’s close to everything you need! You’ll be minutes away from all major food chains, home improvement and retail stores including Ellenton Prime Outlet Mall. It’s only a short drive to enjoy lunch or dinner with some live music on the Manatee River at one of the local hotspots. Willow Walk is conveniently located to I75 and I275 which provides easy work commutes to St. Petersburg, Tampa and Sarasota. Experience endless entertainment options at UTC Mall just 3 exits South, Top Rated Beaches and so much more all within reach! Low HOA Fee, CDD Fee Included in Tax Bill, Not located in a Flood Zone.
